<li class="comment even thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-3265">
<div id="comment-3265" style="position:relative;" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/UserComments">
<div class="comment-author vcard">
<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c83a544d751d380a1f471dd8f700057afa9b23b1afb76b40c0bfcc994066ec68?s=80&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c83a544d751d380a1f471dd8f700057afa9b23b1afb76b40c0bfcc994066ec68?s=160&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-80 photo' height='80' width='80' loading='lazy' decoding='async'/>					<div class="comment-metadata">
<span class="fn" itemprop="creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><a href="http://confeitaria%20de%20sucesso" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Estefane</a></span>						<time>7 de agosto de 2020</time>
<span class="comment-meta">
</span>
</div>
